longBusinessSummary: Foran Mining Corporation engages in the acquisition, exploration, and development of mineral properties. The company primarily explores for copper, zinc, gold, and silver deposits. Its flagship project is the McIlvenna Bay property comprising 38 claims that covers a total area of 20,907 hectares located in east central Saskatchewan. Foran Mining Corporation was incorporated in 1989 and is headquartered in Vancouver, Canada.
